    <h1> Whats Cyber security? </h1>
    <p> so, you hear a lot about cyber security, especially with today's evolving tech. But what exactly is Cyber security? 
        Cyber security is essentially the practice of protecting computers, networks, and personal data from digital attacks or unauthorized access.
        These attacks can aim to steal sensitive information, damage systems, or gain control over accounts.
        Cyber security helps keep information safe, ensures systems run properly, and allows people to use technology and the internet securely in their everyday lives.
    </p>
    
